Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:29.92,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)\a6}製作 ？ 秋月暮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}四月6日 綠洲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.63,0:01:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的車兩三天內真的能修好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.09,0:01:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別是在敷衍我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨中的單色調
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭 幾天沒洗了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗頭又不能用肥皂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 起來 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3}四月7日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭味飄過來了 你頭發上的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要讓我用肥皂洗頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別找借口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 你昨天洗澡了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:04:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么這么問？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:04:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你為什么會不知道沒有洗發液了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛死了 請不要打人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你的頭上的味道就和花田一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你能去買嗎 洗發液
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花田？ 花田的下面是泥土
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說我有泥臭味？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個島是我們的地盤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想從這里過 留下買路錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:05:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不想受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這鞋不錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把老子我給惹毛了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起美發廳的話 還有一間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這的邊好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開店的是個叫Anastacia的外地人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過手藝好 而且是個美女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}如果我不愿意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你在耍我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你這樣是不是太殘酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好不容易近在咫尺了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發尖修剪整齊 這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你是在想Feliciano的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}這種事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你已經太痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}能讓我為你治愈這個傷痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天見過面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Anastacia
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡我的香煙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香煙？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 讓我老公帶在身上的香煙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他總是擅自拿去抽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那煙是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你是從哪里來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就會離開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天下午1點我去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這只是我的誤解 沒有關系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在那時離開房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍著浴巾的男孩開船過來 三個人搶了我的鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是故意不去買的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bruno
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在聽我說話嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫是什么時候開始在這里的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這么說你完全沒有在聽我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是完全...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 洗發液呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 完全沒有在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了 來了圍著浴巾的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢和鞋都被搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以洗發液也沒有買成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫把錢和鞋都扔了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種謊可騙不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看成年人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這么討厭洗頭嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 開什么玩笑...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3}四月8日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算一整天都這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好 情緒有點不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不餓嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去買點什么吃的吧 還有鞋和洗發液
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是沒來得及出門
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什么要這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.69,0:11:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這需要理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是太強硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 我不知道你已經結婚了...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去理發店也是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得那是命運嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得是的 所以來到這里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你沒有在這里等我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有只言片語就這樣結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直非常不安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我... 有喜歡的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也有妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不指這個(婚姻形式)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他喜歡你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該只有我一個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻沒有管你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我 是不會讓你這樣的女孩子悲傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko Malandro
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3}四月9日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是洗頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 別亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關系真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的母親嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我也覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們常說 越是吵架關系越好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過大家都這么說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過阿姨我們家 一直都沒有吵過架 關系很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有問這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去 在這里的水面上有悠然游弋的魚兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不受任何拘束 自由地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你就像那些魚 很美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和這樣的你一起游弋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你... 想做什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我... 該怎么做...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}四月10日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想 是不是可以再更加自由地游弋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說 沒有必要被一片海洋一直束縛著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什么呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說的是 像魚兒一樣更加自由地游弋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 花心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太囂張！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你急什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像傻瓜一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi由我一個人去找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你... 你在說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人去找 怎么找？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人也能行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不需要 不需要Michiko這樣的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:16:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:17:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把搶我的鞋和錢還給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我比賽！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是羅嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個還給你也可以 不過你贏得了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣的根本不是我的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個丟到水里 先拿到的獲勝 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我贏了的話 那個包就歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就要這艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這鞋適合那個孩子 所以拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么知道我住這里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前臺問的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外還有什么方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么請替我向那個孩子問好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想和Bruno在一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我是什么程度的女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這次也是以往一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞到手后就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去性趣 冷淡分手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:19:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這種男人 你能舍棄一切嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己... 你自己又怎么樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然Bruno覺得自己是垂釣者之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實他是魚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終還是想被我釣到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以問一個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他哪里好？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“對不起 果然船還是不能給你”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛滿10歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 恭喜！
